text: Sarah Ann Godlewski (born November 9, 1981) is an American businesswoman and politician. She is the 31st secretary of state of Wisconsin since March 2023. She was the 36th state treasurer of Wisconsin from 2019 to 2023. Godlewski was a candidate for the U.S. Senate in the Democratic primary for the 2022 election before dropping out of the race in July 2022. ==References== Category:1981 births Category:Living people Category:Businesspeople from Madison, Wisconsin Category:Politicians from Madison, Wisconsin Category:Democratic Party (United States) politicians Category:Politicians from Eau Claire, Wisconsin
